{"word":"σκιάζω","slug":"σκιάζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>σκιάζω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:σκιά'><el>σκιά</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to overshadow, shade</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>generally, <i>to overshadow, cover</i>, <b><a href='S:Hesiod'>Hes.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>III. </b><i>to shade in painting</i>, <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}